For launch script, 

1. Open nano editor on terminal

2. Edit code, and CTRL + X for save 

3. Quit with CTRL + O

4. Give access to code with:   chmod +x secure_transfert.sh 

5. launch code with:   ./secure_transfert.sh /home/kali/Desktop/user/TP1/file.txt user@(ip dest) (file destination at other machine)

6. New file create, you can see the file at other machine 
